description:
Anybody can bust on celebrities behind their backs. Only Nick Cannon
and the comics of "Nick Cannon Presents: Wild&#039;n Out" can do it in
their faces. At the new home of sketch and freestyle comedy,
Nick, Dj D-Wrek and a regular troupe of comics bring the street
the stage for this all-out comic throwdown. From Kanye West,
Method Man, Ying Yang Twins and Orlando Jones, to Omarion,
Christina Milian and Kenan Thompson - nobody&#039;s safe on Wild&#039;n Out
(including the audience). Packet with 10 episodes of sketch
comedy, improv games, freestyle comic face-offs and a whole 
DVD filled with special features, 
this is what it means to be "Wild&#039;n Out"!
